code: /** * Aggregates the given element. In the case of a sum aggregator, this method adds the given * value to the sum. * * @param element The element to aggregate. */ void aggregate(T element).

comment: /**  * Resets the internal state of the aggregator. This must bring the aggregator into the same  * state as if it was newly initialized.  */
code: /**  * Resets the internal state of the aggregator. This must bring the aggregator into the same  * state as if it was newly initialized.  */ void reset().
